<i>our time.</i>

96
00:10:05.396 --> 00:10:08.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Scientists call it the Holocene.</i>

97
00:10:14.280 --> 00:10:17.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
