00:11:35.444 --> 00:11:38.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>to capture as much of the sun's energy</i>
<i>as possible,</i>

113
00:11:39.240 --> 00:11:42.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
